<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/tips.css"></head><body><p><b>Compare Jupyter notebooks</b></p><p>To compare any two Jupyter notebooks, select one in the <span class="control">Project</span> tool window, right-click it, and select <span class="control">Compare With</span> from the context menu. In the file system, select a notebook you want to compare to.</p><p>IntelliJ IDEA will show two notebooks and the comparison results in the diff viewer.</p></body></html>